cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DS

This paper discusses the security and efficiency of outsourcing data to the cloud and performing queries over encrypted data. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of hardware-assisted trusted execution environments, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel method for multi-user access control, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed systems (cs.DS).
